Description:
North-Facing Forge Oasis is a Stylish Standout
With an enviable northerly aspect that allows for truly special views of the memorable city skyline, this brand new two bedroom, two bathroom apartment in the Forge complex is one of the best opportunities in the Yarra’s Edge precinct.
With contemporary grace and a considered floorplan which makes the most of the space and views, this 10th floor apartment will have widespread appeal. Sizeable and open lounge and dining includes a dazzling stone kitchen featuring elegant cabinetry and Smeg stainless steel appliances.
There are three access points out to the balcony (from central living and both bedrooms), with this wonderful alfresco zone brilliant to soak in the CBD and Yarra River views as well as out to the rest of the Docklands. Both bedrooms are equipped with built-in robes including the master haven which also delivers an ensuite. Enjoy a sumptuous central bathroom, concealed laundry, heating and cooling, video intercom and a secure car space. Residents also has access to the exclusive Wharf Club with gym, pool and café as well as a private kitchen/dining room and cinema.
Walk to South Wharf promenade with restaurants and bars including Citizen Café and Bar, Melbourne Public, Bangpop, and Munich Brauhaus. You’re also near the Victoria Harbour precinct, Crown Entertainment Complex with world class restaurants, Port Melbourne and South Melbourne attractions, and Southern Cross Station.

Description:
UNIQUE DOCKLANDS RETREAT
You are sure to be impressed by this 2 bedroom residence right in the heart of the revamped District in Docklands. Enter through the huge common quadrangle, via a secure lift, into your own spacious courtyard, perfect for barbecues in summer.
The open plan living zone steps down from the dining to the lounge area, leading out to a spacious private balcony. The contemporary kitchen comprises of stainless steel appliances and granite bench-tops, with loads of cupboard space, natural light, and is ideal for cooking up a storm.
Both generously sized bedrooms include huge built-in robes, and both come with plenty of natural light. They are serviced by a large, modern bathroom, with loads of storage in the vanity and mirrored cupboards. Euro-laundry, split system heating & air-conditioning, modern fixtures & fittings, a secure car park, and a storage cage complete this chic Docklands home.
With its huge courtyard and large balcony, this property is wonderfully situated, set among the revamped District shopping mall, with H & M, plans for a Hoyts Cinemas, Woolworths, and a Docklands school nearby. Especially with public transport, and an array of waterside restaurants on your doorstep, this must see home is perfectly positioned only minutes from the CBD and CityLink.

Description:
LOCATION, LUXURY, LIFESTYLE – all the elements of a great package that you are looking for.
“Exceptional” can only describe the poise, the position and the prestige of this spectacular 4 bedrooms, 2.5-bathroom, 4 car garage, freehold north facing waterfront residence. Designed over several levels to maximise the water views and its immediate WOW factor.
This beautiful architecturally designed 4-level home has energy efficient features such as, floor to ceiling tinted and double-glazed doors and windows for privacy, security, noise reduction and energy efficiency. Private lift to all four levels, this unrivalled masterpiece boasts keyless entry to an automated security system with video intercom, commercial grade reverse cycle ducted heating and air conditioning, electronic blinds throughout, ducted vacuum, poliform fit out to all wardrobes, Clipsal home automation system, computerised garden watering system, a 15m marina berth and direct access to the boulevard.
Level 1 has a cinema room that doubles as a home gym / studio, a laundry, study, plenty of cupboard space and a storeroom that can be used as a wine cellar plus an enormous basement storage area. There is internal access to the spacious 4 car garage with remote control.
Level 2 features the entrance from the street frontage leading to a first-class Miele kitchen with coffee machine, steamer oven, induction cooking, butler’s pantry, wine fridge, integrated fridge / freezer and breakfast bar overlooking the casual living area with bi-fold doors to the north facing alfresco terrace (BBQ kitchen).
Adjoining the kitchen is a formal lounge room and dining area featuring a gas log fireplace leading into a TV room that opens out to a stunning outdoor entertainment area and private terrace with spectacular views overlooking the river.
Level 3 comprises of a spacious north facing master bedroom with a large ensuite and huge WIRs, from the master bedroom you can step out onto your private balcony for a 180-degree views of the river, one of a few houses in the development that has this feature. A separate bathroom with a spa bath and a large shower is available for the rest of the family. Three additional bedrooms are also on this floor with BIR’s and plenty of storage space on this level.
Level 4 is the entertainers level, featuring the 41 sqm rooftop terrace with panoramic views overlooking the Yarra River towards the fantastic lights of Docklands and the CBD. Also located on level 4 is a multi-purpose room that can be utilised as a games room, guest bedroom/bed 5 or just a quiet sun-drenched retreat.

One of the Best Investments in the NewQuay Precinct
With a fabulous 10th floor position in the ‘Gold Tower’ of the exclusive Aqui development, this exceptional north-facing one bedroom apartment promises modern and relaxed living in the NewQuay precinct.
This is a perfect opportunity for first home buyers or those looking to start or build an investment portfolio in the popular Docklands area. The northern orientation of this property gives you fantastic views which are best enjoyed from the balcony over a quiet wine of a summer meal. Inside, the open plan living and meals zone has easy access to the stone kitchen, which is complete with sleek black tapware and stainless steel appliances.
Other great features include a sizeable bedroom with built-in robe, deluxe bathroom, European laundry, reverse cycle heating and cooling, secure intercom, and access to a 25m indoor pool, spa, sauna, gym, library, private meeting rooms, lush rooftop garden, and secure on-site bicycle storage as part of the building.

Description:
Yarra Point brilliance with a waterside location
For buyers who love fantastic space and outstanding quality in the amazing Yarra’s Edge precinct, this wonderfully modern two bedroom residence is the perfect Docklands apartment right on the edge of the iconic Yarra River.
The well-sized open plan living and dining zone is a genuine highlight of this 8th floor residence, with this airy space a dream for everyday relaxing thanks to bright full windows and premium carpet. Sliding doors open out from this central hub which allows residents to access the balcony, which provides a quiet alfresco zone to enjoy after work drinks and your Sunday morning coffee.
The straight line kitchen is made from quality stone and comes with stainless steel Miele appliances. Both bedrooms with BIRs get superb afternoon sun and are excellent rooms to view picturesque sunsets, while further embrace a gorgeous bathroom with floor-to-ceiling tiles, European laundry, ducted heating and cooling, secure intercom, secure car space, and access to RekDek with gym, pool, spa, steam room, and sauna.
In the Yarra’s Edge precinct, you’re not far from South Wharf Promenade with restaurants and bars including Meat Market, Common Man, Gasolina, and West Village NYC, DFO shopping, Crown Casino, Spencer Street trams, and Southern Cross Station.

Description:
Executive Living in Yarra Point
With sweeping 180 degree views of Port Philip Bay, the CBD and a position overlooking the Yarra, how could you resist this striking two bedroom + study home at Yarra's Edge. During the day this wonderful space is bathed in natural sunlight and by night you will be mesmerised by the magnificence of a city skyline that only Melbourne can offer.
Full size open living area maximises both space and natural light with floor to ceiling windows across its entire length, the designer kitchen puts everything at your fingertips including premium Miele appliance, loads of storage space and island bench perfect for soaking up the sunrise over morning breakfast. Each of the bedrooms feature built in wardrobes, smartly positioned off the central hallway, main bathroom and full separate study, whilst the master quarter includes sumptuous his and hers ensuite with deep bath making for a truly harmonious residence.
Further features include central heating and cooling throughout, two secure car spaces, smart energy and connectivity solutions, use of Yarra Point's resident only gymnasium, business centre, and gardens all in addition to membership to the exclusive RekDek featuring heated lap pool, spa, sauna and fully equipped gymnasium.

AMAZING OPPORTUNITY IN DOCKLANDS

Description:
North-Facing Waterside Living has Modern Character
Delivering a northern orientation, high end fittings and fixtures, and a position right alongside the Yarra River as well as being just moments to the excellent South Wharf Promenade, this deluxe two bedroom apartment has an enticing modern resume.
It’s hard not to be impressed by this 4th floor retreat, which offers wonderful outdoor entertaining with a sizeable undercover balcony promising beautiful views of the marina which is perfect at night as the lights of the nearby buildings reflect off the water. This great alfresco space is also large enough to host friends for weekend drinks.
Inside, take advantage of a spacious central living and dining zone which showcases the excellent views, gourmet kitchen with stainless steel Miele appliances, sizeable main bedroom with a built-in robe, 2nd bedroom/study or home office (also with BIR), and a quality, renovated central bathroom with concealed laundry.
Other property extras include ducted heating and cooling, intercom entry, secure car space, and access to RekDek including gym, pool, spa, steam room, and sauna. You’re also positioned close to an IGA X-Press, Capital City Trail, DFO shopping, Crown Casino, and great public transport

Description:
Superb Views and the Luxury of Space
River and city views, spaciousness and a first-class address deliver a lifestyle home you'll be proud to come home to. Welcome to one of South Wharf Drive's exclusive addresses, with three levels of luxurious style and a rooftop terrace for looking out to one of the world's best cities. Enjoy the advantages of inner-city living and the spaciousness so rarely seen this close to the CBD. Two large living zones open onto outdoor living areas, perfect for when you want to relax at home or entertain. With three bedrooms and two bathrooms this works well as an easy-care family home, lock-up-and-leave city address, or work from home in spacious surroundings. Excellent fitout shows in the Miele kitchen, and the north-facing orientation provides natural light through feature windows. A high-spec fitout includes ducted air conditioning, underbench kitchen lighting, integrated fridge-freezer, homed bluestone paving, and water storage. Easy access comes standard here, thanks to your own double garage and on-street parking at your front door. One of South Wharf's best locations, as it's minutes to the heart of the city, there's easy freeway access, DFO shopping close by, and dozens of restaurants and cafes are a riverside stroll away.

Description:
Spacious(108m2) two bedroom apartment with great conditions
This fabulous apartment located on the 12th floor of the iconic Watergate building is ready for you to move straight in or to earn income. With an abundance of internal space as well as stunning views taking in Victoria Harbour, Docklands Park, and through to Port Phillip Bay, this two bedroom, two bathroom apartment with a secure car park is the complete package of relaxed living and appealing Docklands style.
This spacious plan residence is highlighted by a well-sized central lounge and dining zone, with full windows with sleek roller blinds opening out to the generous balcony with the park, bay, and harbour vistas which you can enjoy at all times of the year.
The kitchen is steeped in quality marble and features excellent storage and S/S appliances including a dishwasher, the main bedroom boasts a great walk-in robe as well as a private ensuite. The spacious 2nd bedroom has a study nook and access out the balcony, and is adjoining by the dual access bathroom which also has a laundry. Other appealing apartment extras include ducted heating and cooling, video intercom, secure car space, and access to Watergate facilities including a heated pool, sauna, spa, and gymnasium.
Great location with a tram stop being just downstairs, 500 meters from Southern Cross Station, cafes, restaurants and major shopping precincts within a stone's throw.

Description:
One of the Best Docklands Entertainers on the Market
Sophistically renovated interior with a sensational outdoor courtyard which measures 45 sqm (approx.) that is primed to be used for amazing alfresco entertaining any time of the year, this luxury two bedroom, two bathroom retreat will have you yearning to make the ultimate Docklands change.
We need to begin with the phenomenal outdoor area, which has an abundance of space along with open and covered areas perfect to enjoy come rain, hail, or shine. This sizeable area also has its own access directly to the pool. Inside through the main entry you’ll pass the renovated family bathroom and will be taken directly into the large central lounge and meals hub, with the adjoining gourmet kitchen, functionally added extra pantry area , sumptuous benchtops, breakfast bar, and upgraded stainless steel appliances.
Both bedrooms are equipped with built-in robes and have direct access to the courtyard, which includes the master bedroom with its own gorgeous renovated ensuite. Other extras include a designer main bathroom with laundry, reverse cycle heating and cooling, secure intercom, storage cage, secure car space, and access to a pool, gym, and entertaining area.
Enjoy this excellent NewQuay Precinct location close to The District Docklands, Costco, Victoria Harbour restaurants, supermarkets, Etihad Stadium, and the 30, 75, and 86 trams.
Please contact Charles Finnigan on 0437 204 556 to arrange an exclusive viewing.
